12 Great Stocks for 2016
 by Seeking Alpha | Jan 7, 2016 | Elizabeth Jones, Insights & News, Large Cap, Media Coverage




Media Coverage

 
 
 
 





Home  >  Insights & News  >  Media Coverage

 
 
 

 
 



Overview

 

Elizabeth Jones, Portfolio Manager for the Buffalo Large Cap Fund, was profiled in an article for Money magazine, where she identifies several stocks that can have strong growth potential in 2016.
“Fear of failure drives many mutual fund managers to spread their bets widely. Actively managed U.S. stock funds hold an average of 152 different companies, reports Morningstar. World funds average 225. The stewards of the funds on the following pages are different. They invest in 50 companies or fewer, following their best ideas with conviction—and to great success.” ~ Carolyn Bigda, article author
To access the article click here.

 


